Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.53,0:24:01.53,Default,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1438533,1441536}Next episode preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.13,0:24:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1442137,1446074}One by one, the streets\Nof Paris caught on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.07,0:24:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1446074,1451313}For the trained soldiers of Versailles,\Nthe population of the city was no threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.31,0:24:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1451313,1456985}My siblings with Jules and Jean are doing\Neverything they can to defend our homes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.98,0:24:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1456985,1463392}Finally, on May 28, the last gunfire\Nresounds and the battle is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.39,0:24:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1463392,1465294}Final episode of\N"Isabelle from Paris":
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.29,0:24:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1465294,1468497}"Departure For a New Life".\NPlease look forward to it.
